  "title": "Customer Service Officer (Accommodation)",
  "description": "<p><strong>Industry: Hospitality</strong><br /><strong>Location: East (Company Transport Provided at Tanah Merah MRT)</strong><br /><strong>﻿5-day work week (Mon to Sun)</strong><br /><strong>﻿Rotating Shifts: 8.30am to 5.45pm / 10.45am to 8.00pm</strong></p><p><strong>﻿Job Responsibilities: </strong></p><ul><li>﻿﻿Manage daily villa bookings, amendments, and check-in/out operations.</li><li>Handle guest enquiries, payments, and service recovery when needed.</li><li>Prepare reports, quotations, and billing requests.</li><li>Oversee lost & found items and monitor vehicle registration.</li><li>Provide guests with stay information and assistance during their visit.</li><li>Handle feedback, complaints, and incidents professionally.</li><li>Support Duty Manager and perform ad-hoc tasks assigned by Management.<br /></li></ul><p><strong>Requirements: </strong></p><ul><li>Minimum GCE N level with at least 1 year of relevant experience in a similar capacity</li><li>Customer service oriented</li><li>Possess good interpersonal and communication skills</li><li>Good customer service skills and integrity</li><li>Must be able to perform shift duties and work on weekends and public holidays</li></ul><p>JOB ID: 5WWYR6R3</p><p>Please send your updated CV to <a href=\"mailto:josie.cha@peopleprofilers.com\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\"><strong>josie.cha@peopleprofilers.com</strong></a></p><p>All Successful candidates can expect a very competitive remuneration package and a comprehensive range of benefits.</p><p>We regret that only shortlisted candidates will be notified.<br /><br />EA Personnel: Cha Zi Jing Josie<br />EA Registration No.: R24124843<br />People Profilers Pte Ltd<br />EA Licence Number: 02C4944<br />Tel: <a href=\"#\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\"><strong>6950 9756</strong></a></p>",
